title: #92Noon LIVE from TCO! Wobby/Lombardi/Russo/Leber
description: #92Noon is broadcasting live from the TCO Performance Center! Wobby kicks off the show with My Guys in the Cornfields, football executive and media analyst Michael Lombardi calls in to talk NFL, The Athleric's Michael Russo talks Wild, and Ben Leber swings by the TCO Studios to talk all things purple!
